{
  "stem": "6763.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had some thread hidden away and a needle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I fixed it for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was, you know, very acceptable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it wasn't until much, much later that I found out that she had hidden all of her jewelry in there-- not the jewelry, but stones.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And eventually, that's what saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When did she take that out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She took it out little by little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She took it out at this incident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, well, that's almost like a separate story, our leaving [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Um, we left on our bellies, crawled underneath trains, and hid in the dark in the crevice of tracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when the train came, we got into the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so quick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was given orders, and you just-- there was no time to think, how did I do it?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where did we get on the train?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I know is we got on the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we traveled north to Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just before we arrived in Zagreb-- and Zagreb railroad station had pretty terrible memory to begin with, because that's where we started-- a Gestapo agent got on the train.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, uh, can I see your papers?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We showed him papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the papers where, you know, you had religion in, in those, he said, you're Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, you have our papers, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh, he said, I know you're Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, when we arrive in Zagreb, you are going to follow me to the German comandante, commandat office.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was my brother and I walking ahead, and my mother and father following.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were walking along the station in Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Um, as we were walking, I nudged my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
